You'd be surprised how many people actually do incest; so second cousin incest isn't weird by any means.

Side note on the topic of most popular forms to least forms of actual incest:
Second cousin (very common) -> cousins (common) -> siblings (common) -> aunt/uncle & nephew/niece (common) -> parent-child (uncommon) -> grandparent-grandchild (rare) -> greatgrandparent-greatgrandchild (very rare)
